title: Spend 1 ETH and buy 10 Super Yetis
body:
Heavily discussed in Discord but simply: The project might have some flaws but it still has a bunch of public hype and potential. Proposal is to spend 1 ETH and buy 10 Yetis, with the plan to sell 5 of those in the near term (first few weeks) to at least recoup the 1 ETH investment, then hold the remaining 5 and hope for massive appreciation.

To relate it to BAYC, I bought 8 for 0.08 ETH, and sold 4 for 0.35 ETH each shortly after. The remaining 4 I'm holding are getting offers for between 1.5-4.5 ETH almost daily, and the highest BAYC sale has been 50 ETH. So I think these projects, if picked right, are fairly low downside but potentially very high upside.

At the moment there are just over 3000 Yetis left and demand is increasing fast, so again this is a short proposal because of urgency.
https://opensea.io/collection/superyeti
